          "name": "Animation or live action — which is better for a how-to video?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "It depends on what you are explaining. Software and abstract processes usually work best with animation and screen capture. Physical products and people-driven services work best in live action. Many of our films combine both. We recommend based on your goal — not on our preference."
