          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How does pricing work for a series of tutorials?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "A series is significantly cheaper per video than one-offs. Concept, setup and design are built once, then reused across every episode — so the cost per video drops as the series grows. We quote series as a package with a clear per-video price."
          }
