        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Is script writing included?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Yes. Everything runs in-house — script, storyboard, shoot or animation, voiceover and final cut. You bring the product knowledge; we turn it into a script that explains it simply. You approve the script before production starts."
